      "avalancheActivity": {
        "comment": "The main danger will be wet snow avalanches and gliding avalanches. As the weather warms up during the day, the danger of triggering, especially on sunny slopes, will increase significantly.\n\nHowever, there are still many places in the high alpine regions with blown snow where a small load can trigger a major avalanche. Weak layers in the snowpack are also a problem. If the load exceeds the load-bearing capacity of the deeper Weak layers, a deep and large avalanche can be triggered. There are many such weak layers, especially on axis above the forest.",
        "highlights": "As the weather warms up, the danger of wet snow avalanches has increased. Blowing snow in the high alpine regions!"
