      "weatherForecast": {
        "comment": "Wednesday will clear, with only a few shallow clouds forming during the day. Winds will be weak in the mid mountains. In the high alpine regions, moderate northerly winds will continue at first, weakening during the day. Temperatures will be around 5 \u00b0C at 1500 m and 1 \u00b0C at 2500 m in the middle of the day."
      }
